<h3>Programmatic SEO</h3>
<p>WordPress excels at programmatic SEO. Custom post types, Advanced Custom Fields, and WP_Query let you create thousands of templated pages from structured data. Location pages, product pages, comparison pages, and directory listings scale easily.</p>
<p>Webflow's CMS collections support basic programmatic content, but the 10,000-item limit and 40-collection cap restrict large-scale programmatic builds.</p>
<p><strong>Winner: WordPress</strong> for content at scale. <strong>Webflow</strong> for sites under 5,000 pages.</p>
